cardano/transaction/OutputReference.title: OutputReference
cardano/transaction/OutputReference.description:
An `OutputReference` is a unique reference to an output on-chain. The `output_index`
 corresponds to the position in the output list of the transaction (identified by its id)
 that produced that output

types/datum/CampaignDatum.title: CampaignDatum
types/datum/CampaignDatum.description: The datum for a crowdfunding campaign.

fields.title: name
fields.description: The name of the campaign.

fields.title: goal
fields.description: The funding goal in Lovelace.

fields.title: deadline
fields.description: The deadline for the campaign, as a POSIX timestamp.

fields.title: creator
fields.description: The wallet of the campaign creator.

fields.title: milestone
fields.description: A list representing the milestones of the campaign and their completion status.

fields.title: state
fields.description: The current state of the campaign.

fields.title: fraction
fields.description: The fixed amount of reward tokens distributed per contribution fraction.

types/datum/CampaignState.title: CampaignState
types/datum/CampaignState.description: Represents the possible states of a crowdfunding campaign.

anyOf.title: Initiated
anyOf.description: The initial state when a campaign is first created.

anyOf.title: Running
anyOf.description: The state when a campaign is active and accepting contributions.

anyOf.title: Cancelled
anyOf.description: The state when a campaign has been cancelled.

anyOf.title: Finished
anyOf.description: The state when a campaign has successfully met its goal and ended.

anyOf.title: Released
anyOf.description: The state when funds for a milestone have been released to the creator.

types/datum/ConfigDatum.title: ConfigDatum
types/datum/ConfigDatum.description: The main configuration datum for the entire protocol.

fields.title: fees_address
fields.description: The wallet address where platform fees are collected.

fields.title: fees_amount
fields.description: The amount of the platform fee.

fields.title: fees_asset_class
fields.description: The asset class (policy ID and asset name) of the fee token.

fields.title: spend_address
fields.description: The wallet address for spending-related operations.

fields.title: categories
fields.description: A list of supported project categories.

fields.title: multisig_validator_group
fields.description: The multi-signature group required to validate projects.

fields.title: multisig_refutxoupdate
fields.description: The multi-signature group required to update this configuration datum.

fields.title: cet_policyid
fields.description: The policy ID of the Carbon Emission Token (CET).

fields.title: cot_policyid
fields.description: The policy ID of the Carbon Offsetting Token (COT).

fields.title: dao_policyid
fields.description: The wallet address for the DAO.

types/datum/MarketplaceDatum.title: MarketplaceDatum
types/datum/MarketplaceDatum.description: The datum for an asset listed on the marketplace.

fields.title: owner
fields.description: The wallet of the asset's owner (the seller).

fields.title: amount
fields.description: The price of the asset in Lovelace.

types/datum/ProjectDatum.title: ProjectDatum
types/datum/ProjectDatum.description: The datum for a project submitted for validation.

fields.title: developer
fields.description: The wallet of the project developer.

fields.title: document
fields.description: A hash or identifier for the project's documentation.

fields.title: category
fields.description: The category of the project.

fields.title: asset_name
fields.description: The asset name for the project's unique NFT.

fields.title: fees_amount
fields.description: The fee amount paid for project submission.

fields.title: fees_asset_class
fields.description: The asset class of the fee paid.

types/redeemer/Action.title: Action
types/redeemer/Action.description: A redeemer for the `identification_nft` validator, specifying whether to mint or burn the NFT.

anyOf.title: Mint
anyOf.description: The action to mint the Identification NFT.

anyOf.title: Burn
anyOf.description: The action to burn the Identification NFT.

types/redeemer/CampaignAction.title: CampaignAction
types/redeemer/CampaignAction.description: A redeemer for the `campaign` validator, specifying the action to be taken on a crowdfunding campaign.

anyOf.title: Support
anyOf.description: The action for a backer to contribute funds to a campaign.

anyOf.title: Cancel
anyOf.description: The action to cancel a campaign.

anyOf.title: Finish
anyOf.description: The action to successfully finish a campaign.

anyOf.title: Refund
anyOf.description: The action for a backer to claim a refund from a cancelled campaign.

anyOf.title: Release
anyOf.description: The action for the campaign creator to release milestone-based funds.

types/redeemer/GovernanceRedeemer.title: GovernanceRedeemer
types/redeemer/GovernanceRedeemer.description: A redeemer for the governance validator, specifying the action to be taken on a proposal.

anyOf.title: SubmitProposal
anyOf.description: The action to submit a new proposal.

anyOf.title: VoteProposal
anyOf.description: The action to vote on an existing proposal.

anyOf.title: ExecuteProposal
anyOf.description: The action to execute an approved proposal.

anyOf.title: RejectProposal
anyOf.description: The action to reject a proposal.

anyOf.title: Buy
anyOf.description: The action to purchase an asset from the marketplace.

anyOf.title: Withdraw
anyOf.description: The action for the owner to withdraw their asset from the marketplace.

fields.title: action
fields.description: The action to perform: 0 for accepting a project, 1 for rejecting it.

fields.title: amount
fields.description: The amount of Carbon Offsetting Tokens (COT) to be minted upon project approval.

fields.title: oref
fields.description: The output reference of the UTxO being spent.

types/utils/AssetClass.title: AssetClass
types/utils/AssetClass.description: Represents a specific type of asset, uniquely identified by its policy ID and asset name.

fields.title: policy_id
fields.description: The policy ID of the asset.

fields.title: asset_name
fields.description: The name of the asset.

fields.title: required
fields.description: The minimum number of signatures required for a transaction to be valid.

fields.title: signers
fields.description: A list of the verification key hashes of the authorized signers.

types/utils/Vote.title: Vote
types/utils/Vote.description: Represents the possible voting options for a governance proposal.

anyOf.title: Yes
anyOf.description: A vote in favor of the proposal.

anyOf.title: No
anyOf.description: A vote against the proposal.

anyOf.title: Abstain
anyOf.description: A vote to abstain from the decision.

anyOf.title: Pending
anyOf.description: A placeholder state for a vote that has not yet been cast.

types/wallet/Wallet.title: Wallet
types/wallet/Wallet.description: A wallet type for a non-smart contract address.
